{
  "id": "RAW_caec4982",
  "title": "在 CES 上，我们见到了四十年前和十四年后的电脑｜CES 2026",
  "url": "https://www.ifanr.com/1651506?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=",
  "date": "2026-01-09 18:30:10",
  "author": "马扶摇",
  "siteName": "爱范儿",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>不知道你有没有过这样一种感觉：</p>\n  <p>个人电脑发展了三四十年，产品形态在最近一段时间却仿佛陷入了循环——</p>\n  <p>不是一个薄薄的笔记本，就是一个玻璃镶嵌的机箱。反而是手机、手表这些周边计算设备迎来了大爆发。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651507\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-all-laptops.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1284\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-all-laptops.jpg!720 1284w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-all-laptops-360x224.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-all-laptops-768x479.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/1-all-laptops-1024x638.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1284px) 100vw, 1284px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Best Buy Blog</span></p>\n  <p>当然，<strong>形态的高度统一其实是行业成熟之后不可避免的现象</strong>：成熟，但也无趣。</p>\n  <p>幸运的是，在今年的 CES 上，我们找到了很多跳出固有形态的有趣案例，无论是搞「文艺复兴」还是「推陈出新」，十年前 PC 市场那种勃勃生机、万物竞发的境界犹在眼前。</p>\n  <h2>现代版康懋达：HP EliteBoard G1a</h2>\n  <p>如果说今年 CES 上硬件形态和使用形态「双出彩」的一款产品，我们觉得非惠普演示的 Elite Board G1a 莫属——</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651508\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/2-hp-g1a-side-view.jpeg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"5000\" height=\"2813\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/2-hp-g1a-side-view.jpeg!720 5000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/2-hp-g1a-side-view-360x203.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/2-hp-g1a-side-view-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/2-hp-g1a-side-view-1024x576.jpeg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 5000px) 100vw, 5000px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜惠普</span></p>\n  <p>你没看错，这款和淘宝上 20 块包邮的「高端简约静音办公键鼠套装送清洁刷」如出一辙的产品，<strong>其实是一台完整的电脑主机</strong>，插上屏幕就能直接开机使用。</p>\n  <p>对于很多读者来说，HP Elite Board G1a 看起来很像是那些奇奇怪怪的树莓派集成化产品，但它实际上是一次真正的文艺复兴。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651509\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/3-hp-board-live.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2914\" height=\"1626\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/3-hp-board-live.png!720 2914w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/3-hp-board-live-360x201.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/3-hp-board-live-768x429.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/3-hp-board-live-1024x571.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2914px) 100vw, 2914px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Youtube @PCWorld</span></p>\n  <p>四十四年前的 1982 年，一家叫康懋达（Commodore）的公司同样在拉斯维加斯 CES 上展出了一款个人电脑产品，改变世界的意义丝毫不亚于 APPLE II。</p>\n  <p>那台电脑就是 Commodore 64：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651510\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/4-C64-side.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"4600\" height=\"2600\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/4-C64-side.jpg!720 4600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/4-C64-side-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/4-C64-side-768x434.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/4-C64-side-1024x579.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 4600px) 100vw, 4600px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Wikipedia</span></p>\n  <p>在那个使用 CLI 界面的 8 位机（8-bit computer）时代，这种集成键盘式设计是电脑的绝对主流。</p>\n  <p><strong>也就是说，虽然惠普将 Elite Board G1a 定义为「下一代 AI PC」，但它实际上是个文艺复兴级别的一体式电脑。</strong></p>\n  <p>当然，尽管形态复古，Elite Board G1a 的硬件配置一点都不复古。</p>\n  <p>HP Elite Board G1a 搭载 AMD 锐龙 AI 5/7 300 系列处理器，可以选配到 64+2TB 的存储组合，NPU 算力最高可达 50 TOPS。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651511\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/5-hp-board-hands-on.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2908\" height=\"1630\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/5-hp-board-hands-on.png!720 2908w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/5-hp-board-hands-on-360x202.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/5-hp-board-hands-on-768x430.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/5-hp-board-hands-on-1024x574.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2908px) 100vw, 2908px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Youtube @PCMag</span></p>\n  <p>同时锐龙 AI 300 也给 Elite Board G1a 带来了 Radeon 800 系显卡，让这块「键盘」的最高输出规格来到了 8K 60Hz 和 4K 120/240Hz。</p>\n  <p>换句话说，用它玩点轻度游戏也不是不行——毕竟它是带主动散热的。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651512\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/6-hp-board-vent.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2912\" height=\"1632\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/6-hp-board-vent.png!720 2912w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/6-hp-board-vent-360x202.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/6-hp-board-vent-768x430.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/6-hp-board-vent-1024x574.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2912px) 100vw, 2912px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Youtube @PCWorld</span></p>\n  <p>只不过惠普并没有将 Elite Board G1a 标榜成一台移动电脑。虽然它内置了一块 32 瓦时的电池，也支持给便携显示器供电，但长时间离电使用还是比较难的，更多是做备用电源。</p>\n  <p>接口方面，HP Elite Board G1a 有两种可选配置：双 USB-C 接口，或者不可拆卸电源线 + 双 USB-C 接口，主打一个办公够用就行。</p>\n  <p>同时附赠一个预先配对好的蓝牙鼠标，标榜办公室或书桌上的「开箱即用」——</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651513\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/7-hp-board-heat-sink.jpeg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2914\" height=\"1634\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/7-hp-board-heat-sink.jpeg!720 2914w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/7-hp-board-heat-sink-360x202.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/7-hp-board-heat-sink-768x431.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/7-hp-board-heat-sink-1024x574.jpeg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2914px) 100vw, 2914px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Youtube @PCWorld</span></p>\n  <p>比较可惜的是，惠普尚未公布 Elite Board G1a 的具体售价以及上市日期，目前只知道会在年内开售。</p>\n  <p>一台<strong>比 NUC 更集成、比 Mac mini 更便携</strong>的 Windows AIO PC，你会感兴趣吗？</p>\n  <h2>皮克斯台灯远亲：ThinkBook Plus Gen 7 Auto Twist</h2>\n  <p>那个联想专门用来测试各种新硬件理念的 ThinkBook Plus 系列，今年又有新东西看了。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651514\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/8-tb-twist-front.jpeg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/8-tb-twist-front.jpeg!720 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/8-tb-twist-front-360x203.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/8-tb-twist-front-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/8-tb-twist-front-1024x576.jpeg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Mashable</span></p>\n  <p>虽然从外观上说，ThinkBook Plus Gen 7 Auto Twist 平平无奇，不如 ThinkPad Rollable XD 与拯救者 Pro Rollable XD 那么吸睛，但它解决了一个用笔记本电脑时候的最大懒点——</p>\n  <p>需要伸手翻开屏幕。</p>\n  <p>是的，今年的 ThinkBook Plus Gen 7 Auto Twist 主打的功能点就是这块<strong>电机驱动的转轴</strong>，可以实现<strong>自动开关盖</strong>和<strong>屏幕智能跟随</strong>：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651515\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/9-tb-twist.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"538\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/9-tb-twist.gif 960w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/9-tb-twist-360x202.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/9-tb-twist-768x430.gif 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Youtube @Engadget</span></p>\n  <p>只需要轻轻敲两下 A 面的扶手处，ThinkBook Plus Gen 7 Auto Twist 就能在两秒钟内平滑地翻开屏幕，解决了曾经轻薄本难以单手开盖的世纪难题。</p>\n  <p>而在智能跟随方面，它的实现方式堪称是当年 iMac G4 的终极进化版。</p>\n  <p>只需要在程序里面选定要跟随的人脸，电脑就会在使用过程中始终让屏幕朝向选定的人，并<strong>自动调节左右和俯仰</strong>：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651516\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/10-tb-twist-2.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"538\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/10-tb-twist-2.gif 960w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/10-tb-twist-2-360x202.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/10-tb-twist-2-768x430.gif 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Youtube @Engadget</span></p>\n  <p>只不过根据现场的体验，ThinkBook Plus Gen 7 Auto Twist 的电机加速曲线和屏幕稳定性都还没有达到最佳效果，可能受限于机身尺寸的缘故，进行俯仰时会有一些晃动。</p>\n  <p>此外，这么「灵动」的设备自然也缺不了 AI 功能，联想除了给 ThinkPlus Gen 7 Auto Twist 加入了可视化 AI 助手之外，还提供了一个<strong>屏幕随动翻译</strong>的用法——</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651517\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/11-tb-twist-3.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"538\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/11-tb-twist-3.gif 960w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/11-tb-twist-3-360x202.gif 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/11-tb-twist-3-768x430.gif 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Youtube @Engadget</span></p>\n  <p>具体参数配置方面，ThinkBook Plus Gen 7 Auto Twist 搭载了一块 2.8K 120Hz 的 14 寸 OLED 屏幕，以及刚刚发布的 Core Ultra Series 3 系列处理器，和一块 75Wh 的电池。</p>\n  <p>大家比较关心的存储方面，最高可以选配到 32+2TB 的组合；I/O 对于一台 14 寸笔记本来说也比较丰富，两个雷雳 4 和两个全尺寸的 USB-A 3.2 接口，机身总重在 1.4 千克左右，售价和开售日期未定。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651518\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/12-tb-twist-side.jpeg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2040\" height=\"1360\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/12-tb-twist-side.jpeg!720 2040w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/12-tb-twist-side-360x240.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/12-tb-twist-side-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/12-tb-twist-side-1024x683.jpeg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2040px) 100vw, 2040px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜TheVerge</span></p>\n  <p>总之，ThinkBook Plus Gen 7 Auto Twist 是我们在 CES 2026 上看到的为数不多的几个既「好玩」也「好动」的电脑了，对于一些会议或商旅场景来说，它应该会很适合。</p>\n  <h2>苏妈也有 AI 专用机了：AMD Ryzen AI Halo</h2>\n  <p>伴随着今年英伟达 Spark 的陆续发货，如同爱范儿在此前有关 Mac Studio 集群跑 AI 那篇文章中的结论一样：一系列「本地 AI 专用小型机」正在慢慢出现，形成一个颇具规模的市场。</p>\n  <p>而 AMD 终于在本次 CES 上拿出了对标英伟达 DGX Spark 的产品，一台比电视盒子稍大的<strong>一体式微型 AI 工作站</strong>—— AMD Ryzen AI Halo。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651519\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/13-AMD-Halo-1.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/13-AMD-Halo-1.png!720 2560w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/13-AMD-Halo-1-360x203.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/13-AMD-Halo-1-768x432.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/13-AMD-Halo-1-1024x576.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Wccftech</span></p>\n  <p>和 DGX Spark 一样，Ryzen AI Halo 的定义也是一个「本地 AI 开发平台」，旨在加速小规模或个人用户的 AI 开发和 AI 工作流程。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651520\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14-AMD-AI-Halo-live.jpeg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2700\" height=\"2025\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14-AMD-AI-Halo-live.jpeg!720 2700w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14-AMD-AI-Halo-live-360x270.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14-AMD-AI-Halo-live-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/14-AMD-AI-Halo-live-1024x768.jpeg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2700px) 100vw, 2700px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜TheVerge</span></p>\n  <p>Ryzen AI Halo 在迷你的机身里提供了完整的 AMD ROCm 7.2.2 支持，针对 LM Studio、ComfyUI 等主流开发工具提供优化，也支持包括 GPT-OSS、FLUX.2、SDXL 在内的多数主流模型。</p>\n  <p>参数方面，Ryzen AI Halo 会标配 AMD Ryzen Max+ 395，一颗 16 核 32 线程的 5.1GHz 4nm FinFET 处理器，支持最高 128GB 的 LPDDR5X-8533 内存。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651521\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/15-AMD-Halo-iternal.png!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/15-AMD-Halo-iternal.png!720 2560w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/15-AMD-Halo-iternal-360x203.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/15-AMD-Halo-iternal-768x432.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/15-AMD-Halo-iternal-1024x576.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜AMD</span></p>\n  <p>比较可惜的是，AMD 在 CES 现场并未公布 Ryzen AI Halo 的具体售价，仅宣布计划于今年第二季度上市。</p>\n  <p>不过从产品参数来看，<strong>AMD 似乎倾向于走一条性价比路线</strong>，大概率会和 DGX Spark 在关键 SKU 的定价上展开竞争。</p>\n  <h2>给 Win 用户的 iMac：Yoga AIO i Aura Edition</h2>\n  <p>对于很多人来说，「Windows 一体机」已经是一个很遥远的词汇了。</p>\n  <p>不像苹果的 iMac 那样自带装饰属性，Windows 一体机往往卡在「便携不如笔记本、性能不如塔式机箱、装饰性不如独立显示器」的尴尬区间里，在过去几年的个人用户市场里销声匿迹。</p>\n  <p>但联想觉得 Windows 一体机还没有结束。</p>\n  <p>在本次 CES 上，除了上面和之前提到的各种奇妙笔记本之外，联想还带来了 Yoga 系列最新的一体机式电脑：Yoga AIO i Aura Edition。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651522\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/16-yoga-aura-promo.jpeg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2475\" height=\"1440\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/16-yoga-aura-promo.jpeg!720 2475w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/16-yoga-aura-promo-360x209.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/16-yoga-aura-promo-768x447.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/16-yoga-aura-promo-1024x596.jpeg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2475px) 100vw, 2475px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Lenovo</span></p>\n  <p>实际上，除了形态像大家最熟悉的 iMac 之外，我们可以在 Yoga AIO i Aura Edition 上看到非常多过去的影子——</p>\n  <p>比如这个镁铝合金的隐藏式机身，就非常有曾经微软 Surface Studio 的神韵：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651523\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/17-yoga-aura-back.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"2851\" height=\"1604\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/17-yoga-aura-back.jpg!720 2851w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/17-yoga-aura-back-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/17-yoga-aura-back-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/17-yoga-aura-back-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2851px) 100vw, 2851px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜Lenovo</span></p>\n  <p>但如果你对于 PC 行业的记忆更久远一些的话，你其实会发现，相比 Surface，Yoga AIO i Aura Edition 的神态其实更像是苹果推出过的透明支架款 Cinema Display：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651524\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/18-apple-cinema-display.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"920\" height=\"840\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/18-apple-cinema-display.jpg!720 920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/18-apple-cinema-display-360x329.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/18-apple-cinema-display-768x701.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 920px) 100vw, 920px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜iGotOffer</span></p>\n  <p>但 Yoga AIO i Aura Edition 的素质就不是二十年前的 Cinema Display 能够望其项背的了。</p>\n  <p>联想给它上了一块 <strong>32 寸 4K 165Hz OLED</strong> 屏幕，最高可以选配到今年新的 Panther Lake Core Ultra X7 处理器，是字面意义上的「好看又强悍」。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651525\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/19-yoga-aura-stand.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3000\" height=\"1684\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/19-yoga-aura-stand.jpg!720 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/19-yoga-aura-stand-360x202.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/19-yoga-aura-stand-768x431.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/19-yoga-aura-stand-1024x575.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜PCMag Australia</span></p>\n  <p>同时，机身下面的透明亚克力支架作用远不止展示 logo，同时还是一个拥有丰富自定义选项的<strong>系统通知灯</strong>，以及机身内置的<strong>哈曼卡顿音响的氛围灯带</strong>：</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651526\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20-yoga-aura-live.jpeg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"3000\" height=\"1684\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20-yoga-aura-live.jpeg!720 3000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20-yoga-aura-live-360x202.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20-yoga-aura-live-768x431.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/20-yoga-aura-live-1024x575.jpeg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜PCMag Australia</span></p>\n  <p>根据联想的现场介绍，Yoga AIO i Aura Edition 的灯带除了显示通知和作为音响跑马灯之外，还可以识别屏幕显示内容打出背景光，用类似屏幕挂灯「前后分光」的原理，给用户营造沉浸式环境效果。</p>\n  <p>只不过和 iMac 定位家庭电脑不一样，Yoga AIO i Aura Edtion 主打的市场是创意工作室和艺术类用户。</p>\n  <p><strong>它的起售价为 2399 美元</strong>（约合人民币 16700 元），预计于今年第二季度上市。</p>\n  <h2>「后摩尔定律」时代的电脑将何去何从</h2>\n  <p>总的来说，今年的 CES 对于 PC 类产品来说，主打的关键词就是「文艺复兴」和「形态创新」。</p>\n  <p>厂商们要么试着用最新的技术重新诠释过去的美学，要么继续探索柔性屏和卷轴屏电脑的边界。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651527\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/21-wm-legion-rollable-3.jpg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"4096\" height=\"3072\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/21-wm-legion-rollable-3.jpg!720 4096w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/21-wm-legion-rollable-3-360x270.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/21-wm-legion-rollable-3-768x576.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/21-wm-legion-rollable-3-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 4096px) 100vw, 4096px\"></p>\n  <p>哪怕我们可以说这是由于用户审美是一个圈导致的，但在这种产品形态集体回潮的背后，实际上是 PC 性能瓶颈期的逼近。</p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651528\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/22-the-moore-curve.jpeg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"1214\" height=\"815\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/22-the-moore-curve.jpeg!720 1214w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/22-the-moore-curve-360x242.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/22-the-moore-curve-768x516.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/22-the-moore-curve-1024x687.jpeg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1214px) 100vw, 1214px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 图｜ExtremeTech</span></p>\n  <p>虽然「摩尔定律已死」的说法有些过于夸大其词，但不能否认的是：</p>\n  <p><strong>伴随着最近一个十年里生产方式、消费方式和软件工具的急剧细分化，现在消费者选择一台电脑的主要参考指标早就不只纯粹的性能了——</strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1651529\" src=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/23-dell-xps-13.jpeg!720\" alt=\"\" width=\"4032\" height=\"3024\" srcset=\"https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/23-dell-xps-13.jpeg!720 4032w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/23-dell-xps-13-360x270.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/23-dell-xps-13-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/23-dell-xps-13-1024x768.jpeg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 4032px) 100vw, 4032px\"></p>\n  <p><span style=\"color: #999999;\">▲ 号称「最美 Windows 笔电」的戴尔 XPS 13｜Notebookcheck</span></p>\n  <p>比如 iMac 本身的性能并不出众，但优秀的质价比和产品形态让它在家用和商用市场有着难以撼动的地位；戴尔 XPS 和 LG Gram 也曾经为了设计而舍弃过很多配置参数，依然是 Win 本中的口碑佼佼者。</p>\n  <p>因此，我们觉得：2026 年可能是传统 PC 最艰难的一年，但也可能是个性化 PC 最有趣的一年——</p>\n  <p><strong>在处理器和显卡的边际效益都在递减的时候，形态创新会是唯一的出路。</strong></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文分析了 CES 2026 上惠普、联想、AMD 等厂商推出的多款创新 PC 产品，指出在摩尔定律瓶颈下，形态创新和个性化将是未来 PC 发展的主要趋势。",
